==Description==
<tt><nowiki>{{bk-big|nation|variant|size=optional|name=optional}}</nowiki></tt>

Produces a flag icon attached to a wikilinked men's national basketball team article.  This differs from [[Template:Bk]], making the flag icon larger and putting the team name underneath the flag.  This style is used for certain event results tables.

;Parameters
*''nation'' — Use either the name of the nation or the three-letter country code as used by [[FIBA]]
*''variant'' (optional) — Specifies an alternate (historical) flag to use.  This parameter is documented by the appropriate template in [[:Category:国家资料模板]].
*''name'' (optional) — Can be used to change the wikilink display text

==Examples==
{| class="wikitable"
|-
| <tt><nowiki>{{bk-big|Argentina}}</nowiki></tt> ||align=center| {{bk-big|Argentina}}
|-
| <tt><nowiki>{{bk-big|LTU}}</nowiki></tt> ||align=center| {{bk-big|LTU}}
|-
| <tt><nowiki>{{bk-big|Spain|1939}}</nowiki></tt> ||align=center| {{bk-big|Spain|1939}}
|}

